cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with the task of Neural Machine Translation. Additionally, it may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of state-of-the-art algorithms and models for NMT. The use of limited but almost correct parallel corpus may also make it relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves the optimization of translation performance.
